{"tid":1948702,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"穆斯林教會疫情下堅持聚會","createTime":"2020-03-29T07:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T08:31:41.000Z","uid":303304,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f3308adf2e7e8494d65b0bede0d87aa81ae9806b","tid":1948702,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1jyMzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1jyMzO.png&h=f436e476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港府禁止多於4人聚會的命令，今日（29日）凌晨生效。惟有穆斯林教會不滿安排，指他們每日需禱告5次，政府的新措施變相令他們無法順利舉行禱告儀式，教會秘書已去信特首林鄭月娥申請豁免，揚言若政府拒讓信眾在保持一定距離下拜神禱告，計劃將儀式移師特首辦門外。<br />\n<br />\n會址位於深水埗的穆斯林教會「HAZRAT SIDDIQUE AKBAR SOCIETY」，其教會秘書沙積昨日去信林鄭月娥，稱該教會每日需禱告5次，如今政府施加不多於4人聚集的限制，嚴重影響禱告安排；即他們只能每次讓4人進入面積達1,600平方呎的會址，每次需時約半小時，「星期日仲可以，但星期一大家要返工，根本無可能咁等。」<br />\n<br />\n沙積稱，因會址面積大，單是禱告位置已多達逾千平方呎，故教會可安排每4人一組禱告，每組分隔多於1.5米，全程戴上口罩；信眾進場前，教會會為他們量度體溫；儀式完結後，信眾便會離開；會址亦只於禱告時開放，希望獲政府豁免禁聚令。他認為此舉已可防範病毒傳播，亦質疑為何餐廳等食肆每枱分隔1.5米後，可讓食客內進用膳，「點解我哋唔可以？」他稱若政府無視他們的訴求，「如果政府唔畀，（我哋）會去到林鄭（特首辦）門口禱告。」<br />\n<br />\n沙積又稱，灣仔及尖沙嘴亦有多間大大小小的穆斯林教會，均需每日5次舉行禱告儀式。他批評政府的新措施對他們影響甚大，希望政府盡快回應。<br />\n<br />\nsource: apple"},{"pid":"fbc578d0e04d2a716a608103ce203cffa1757704","tid":1948702,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"感謝穆斯林手足堅持攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e2a9be2e37221cd1a01496bf6c0a40a63d8e37","tid":1948702,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"班狗唔好鳩縮呀<br />\n拉人未"},{"pid":"acf9ebfda45c231125b319b74e165524886fc6db","tid":1948702,"uid":346806,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"揚言若政府拒讓信眾在保持一定距離下拜神禱告，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">計劃將儀式移師特首辦門外。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"175b1acc1ce11be2a50a99131f78d3e3e88f0d19","tid":1948702,"uid":254183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"攬炒大隊<br />\n阿拉胡阿克巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeeac080904b96c4a05d2017e0d43435264dcaf","tid":1948702,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"警察對於穆斯林變死狗"},{"pid":"2092168b5a24b44fc260caa0581ad9ea2b0a21e6","tid":1948702,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeeeac080904b96c4a05d2017e0d43435264dcaf","tid":1948702,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"警察對於穆斯林變死狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係死狗"},{"pid":"8edfd74911eb3aafd7a162ec6ca8452b84594087","tid":1948702,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eeeeac080904b96c4a05d2017e0d43435264dcaf","tid":1948702,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"警察對於穆斯林變死狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:40:27.000Z","msg":"今日對賓印已經死狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgwUv25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgwUv25.png&h=f13fa0d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0764e2c17b456b066ce0a575b3ad801fb67c6513","tid":1948702,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"支持蛜自我毀滅<br />\n呢啲蛜除咗虐待女人同放炸彈<br />\n仲識做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1898c12ffa95cab8eb0edaf250091b3c83f2bfa","tid":1948702,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8edfd74911eb3aafd7a162ec6ca8452b84594087","tid":1948702,"uid":303304,"like":